\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n+3}
\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n+3} = \sum_{n=3}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n}
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n}
\sum_{n = 0}^\infty \frac{1}{n+3}
\iff \int_0^\infty \frac{1}{x+3}
\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n + 3}
\int_1^\infty \frac{1}{n+3}\text{d}x
 \lim_{t\rightarrow\infty} \int_1^t \frac{1}{n+3}\text{d}n = \lim_{t\rightarrow\infty} \ln(t+3) = \infty
